<br>
    we dont get a Epic 2 we get various upgrades to our existing epic. like whats our epic now? 14/24 or something whatever. ok so we go and get 4 quest pieces from lets say Velious and combind them into our scabard and that creates and new item that is combined with our existing epic will create a new epic that is lets say 14/20<br>
<br>
     or you are higher up on the food chain and you get your 4 pieces from Luclin (aten, emp whatever) instead of velious, and combined them you might get something like a 16/18 epic.<br>
<br>
   or you get your parts from tier 4 (planes in POP) and you might get a 18/16 epic.<br>
<br>
this way until you get the highest epic upgrade items possible you can always up grade your epic, just get the 4 quest parts combined them then combined that with your epic.<br>
<br>
I dont know, sounds like a good idea though.<br>
<br>
--oh and you could combined different ones like the teir 4 part with Velious part with 2 from Luclin or something to make like 18/22 with more stats. or something. they would just have to make a bunch of alt epics and when you combined certain epic quest parts you get that epic.  <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.lvcm.com/gforce/avs/aakla.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
